<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        .head {
            background-color: #333333; /* Black-gray color */
            color: white; /* White text for contrast */
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40vh;
            background-image: url('../images/MainPage.png'); /* Ensure text is readable */
            background-size: cover; /* Ensures the image covers the entire div */
            background-position: center; /* Centers the image */
            color: white; /* Makes the text stand out on the background */
            padding: 50px; /* Adds space inside the div */
            text-align: center; /* Centers the text */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="head">
        <h1>Educational Technology Apps</h1>
        <h2>How can technology enhance your learning experience?</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Creating practical tutorials to support and enhance the effective use of educational technology in teaching and learning.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="image">

    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                Educational Technology Tools
            </h2>
            <p>
                Educational technology applications are designed to enhance the learning process by integrating digital tools.
                They help both educators and learners by offering interactive content and promoting collaboration.
                These applications aim to improve learning outcomes by incorporating technology into everyday educational experiences.
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("EdTechPage", "Home")">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                E-Evaluation Tools
            </h2>
            <p>
                These tools include formative and summative assessments, quizzes, rubrics, surveys, and analytics platforms that provide
                insights into student progress. Modern educational technologies integrate AI-driven assessments,
                adaptive learning platforms, and real-time feedback systems to enhance personalized learning
                and data-driven decision-making. By utilizing evaluation tools, educators can improve teaching strategies and ensure
                better student achievement.
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("EEvaluationPage", "Home")">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h2>
                AI in Education
            </h2>
            <p>
                AI in education empowers teachers by personalizing learning experiences for each student.
                It helps educators tailor lessons to individual needs and automates time-consuming tasks such as grading and assessments.
                With AI, teachers can provide real-time feedback, track student progress more efficiently, and enhance classroom engagement.
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("AIInEducationPage", "Home")">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 
